            "type": "text",
            "text": "For experienced API teams, adding voice capabilities requires robust tools. The Chatterbox voice api offers a scalable solution for text-to-speech and streaming, enabling efficient integration into production workflows. This guide focuses on practical implementation without unnecessary theory."
